        <h2 class="style-guide">Typography</h2>
        <h4>Merriweather</h4>
        <p>Merriweather is an open source serif font designed to be a text face that is pleasant to read on screens. Currently there are 4 styles: Regular, Light, Bold and Black with Italic styles for each of these weights. Headings (1-5) use Merriweather Bold.</p>
        <h4>Source Sans Pro</h4>
        <p>Source Sans Pro is an open source sans serif font with a variety of weights. All text that does not use Merriweather uses Source Sans Pro.</p>
