        <h2 class="style-guide">Colors</h2>
        <h4>Background Colors</h4>
        <p>There are 3 main colors for backgrounds: primary-dark, gray-lightest and gray-lightest-light. White is not used as a background color.</p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#112e51"><br></div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#f1f1f1"><br></div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#eeeeee"><br></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Primary dark is reserved for the header and footer.</div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Gray lightest is used for the main background.</div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Gray lightest light is used for card backgrounds.</div>
        </div>
        <h4>Text Colors</h4>
        <p>All text is in the base color, including headings, p tags and body.</p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#212121"><br></div>
        </div>
        <h4>Link Colors</h4>
        <p>There are links on light and dark backgrounds. Links on light backgrounds change color in the active and hover state. Links on dark backgrounds change color only in the hover state.</p>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#0071bc"><br></div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#4c2c92"><br></div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#3e94cf"><br></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Primary is for links on light backgrounds.</div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Visit is for links that are in a visited state on light backgrounds.</div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Focus is for links that are in the hover state on light backgrounds.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#f1f1f1"><br></div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes" style="background-color:#aeb0b5"><br></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Gray lightest is for links that are in a normal or visited state on a dark background.</div>
          <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-sm-3 colors-boxes">Gray light is for links that are in the hover state on a dark background.</div>
