        <h2 class="style-guide">Links</h2>
        <p>Links by default do not have any style. On a light background, When links are in a hover state, the underline will appear and the color will change.</p>
        <h5>Examples</h5>
        <a href="#">This</a> is a link on light background.
        <br>
        <a class="visited" href="#">This</a> is a visited link.
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-sm-6">
            <div class="dark-background">
              <a href="#">This</a> is a link on a dark background.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <hr class="blue">

        <h2 class="style-guide">Buttons</h2>
        <p>Buttons should be flat and change color in a hover state.</p>
